wdi-EN.ATM.METH.EG.ZS.def: Methane emissions from energy processes are emissions from the production, handling, transmission, and combustion of fossil fuels and biofuels.
wdi-EN.ATM.METH.EG.ZS.name: Energy related methane emissions
wdi-EN.ATM.METH.EG.ZS.source: World Bank staff estimates from original source: European Commission, Joint Research Centre (JRC)/Netherlands Environmental Assessment Agency (PBL). Emission Database for Global Atmospheric Research (EDGAR): http://edgar.jrc.ec.europa.eu/.
